    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/7cd4c503a44b46db59a88c2533f56eeb.poster.avif?t=1693218522\" width=628 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/7cd4c503a44b46db59a88c2533f56eeb.webm?t=1693218522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/7cd4c503a44b46db59a88c2533f56eeb.mp4?t=1693218522\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>                       <strong><i>RoFIsh: Prelude</i></strong> is a first person adventure about a cat named Stas,        <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.webp?t=1693218522\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.poster.avif?t=1693218522\" class=\"bb_img\" width=15 height=15 /></picture></span><br>                                         trying to escape an island after a shipwreck.<br>                                        Throughout the game you will get to witness<br>            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.webp?t=1693218522\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.poster.avif?t=1693218522\" class=\"bb_img\" width=15 height=15 /></picture></span>           a deliberately clawchéd plot, absurd dialogs and drunkard crabs.<br><br>                                                     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/0deacbcebab9a806d6bb6b2946950805.poster.avif?t=1693218522\" width=180 height=66 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/0deacbcebab9a806d6bb6b2946950805.webm?t=1693218522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>               Upon waking up Stas faces the fact that his ship is broken and he has to fix it.<br>                      But where would he get supplies and tools on an uninhabited island?          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.webp?t=1693218522\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.poster.avif?t=1693218522\" class=\"bb_img\" width=15 height=15 /></picture></span><br>          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.webp?t=1693218522\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.poster.avif?t=1693218522\" class=\"bb_img\" width=15 height=15 /></picture></span>                                                 Stas sure is lucky!<br>                  Because after the virulent storm the sea dwellers have acquired sentience<br>                            and are ready to help….for something in return, of course =)<br>                                                                                                                                         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.webp?t=1693218522\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.poster.avif?t=1693218522\" class=\"bb_img\" width=15 height=15 /></picture></span><br>                              Help the natives, complete mini-games and solve puzzles.<br>                Stas is a fisherman and his fishing rod will help him solve a lot of problems =)<br>    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.webp?t=1693218522\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.poster.avif?t=1693218522\" class=\"bb_img\" width=15 height=15 /></picture></span>                     Upgrade it, collect bait and use it to catch an assortment of fish<br>                                                  and other inhabitants of the sea.<br>                     But be very observant, some of them require a different approach :)<br><br>                                                     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/2cc49381015cc9c534001257554b1f98.apng?t=1693218522\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/2cc49381015cc9c534001257554b1f98.poster.avif?t=1693218522\" class=\"bb_img\" width=180 height=66 /></picture></span><br><br>        <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.webp?t=1693218522\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.poster.avif?t=1693218522\" class=\"bb_img\" width=15 height=15 /></picture></span>                     - A warm and welcoming tropical island <i>(about +30 С°)</i><br>                                             - Pleasant voxel graphics <i>(we hope:)</i>                                    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.webp?t=1693218522\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.poster.avif?t=1693218522\" class=\"bb_img\" width=15 height=15 /></picture></span><br>                <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.webp?t=1693218522\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.poster.avif?t=1693218522\" class=\"bb_img\" width=15 height=15 /></picture></span>                           - Small mini-games <i>(like, really tiny)</i><br>                                     - Mini-games <i>(almost the same as small ones)</i><br>                                           - Big mini-games <i>(like, freaking <strong>HUGE</strong>)</i>                                           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.webp?t=1693218522\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.poster.avif?t=1693218522\" class=\"bb_img\" width=15 height=15 /></picture></span><br>                                      - Deep plot <i>(not a Mariana Trench, but close)</i><br>      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.webp?t=1693218522\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.poster.avif?t=1693218522\" class=\"bb_img\" width=15 height=15 /></picture></span>                                           - Satire <i>(jokes out the wazoo)</i><br>                            - Memorable characters <i>(well, I don’t think I forgot anyone)</i>             <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.webp?t=1693218522\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.poster.avif?t=1693218522\" class=\"bb_img\" width=15 height=15 /></picture></span><br>                     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.webp?t=1693218522\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/87602c53e69f85b0ae677a695c45dbe6.poster.avif?t=1693218522\" class=\"bb_img\" width=15 height=15 /></picture></span> - Memes, references and reminiscences <i>(a big, smart word, google it)</i><br>                                                  - You can play as a cat (=^･^=)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/83152c62b9cb015a9ff89a23546ac9ab.poster.avif?t=1693218522\" width=620 height=175 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1731230/extras/83152c62b9cb015a9ff89a23546ac9ab.webm?t=1693218522\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
